{%- comment -%}
  ps-testimonials.liquid — Customer reviews display powered by Judge.me.

  Reviews are managed entirely through the Judge.me app:
    Admin → Apps → Judge.me Reviews → Reviews (pending/published)

  Stan's workflow:
    1. Customer submits a review (post-purchase email or Write a Review button)
    2. Review appears in Judge.me → Reviews → Pending
    3. Stan approves it → it immediately shows on the product page AND here
    4. No manual copying. One approval = everywhere.

  The jdgm-all-reviews-widget pulls ALL published reviews across all products.
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="ps-testimonials" id="ps-testimonials">
  <div class="ps-testimonials-inner">

    <div class="ps-testimonials-header">
      <div class="ps-section-tag ps-reveal">⭐ Customer Love</div>
      <h2 class="ps-section-h2 ps-reveal ps-rd1">What Our <em>Customers Say!</em></h2>
      <p class="ps-testimonials-sub ps-reveal ps-rd2">Real words from real people who've brought a little Iowa into their homes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ps-jdgm-wrap ps-reveal ps-rd2">
      <div id="judgeme_all_reviews" class="jdgm-widget jdgm-all-reviews-widget" data-per-page="6"></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
.ps-testimonials { background: var(--lav-xlight); padding: 6rem 2rem 5rem; }
.ps-testimonials-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
.ps-testimonials-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.ps-testimonials-sub { font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--lav-ink); max-width: 480px; margin: .75rem auto 0; line-height: 1.5; }
.ps-jdgm-wrap { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }

/* Judge.me widget overrides to match Papa Stan's theme */
.ps-testimonials .jdgm-widget { font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif !important; }
.ps-testimonials .jdgm-rev-widg__title { font-family: 'Luckiest Guy', cursive !important; font-size: 1.4rem !important; letter-spacing: .04em !important; color: var(--lav-ink) !important; }
.ps-testimonials .jdgm-write-rev-link { background: var(--lav) !important; border-color: var(--lav) !important; border-radius: 30px !important; font-family: 'Luckiest Guy', cursive !important; letter-spacing: .06em !important; }
.ps-testimonials .jdgm-write-rev-link:hover { background: var(--lav-dark) !important; }
.ps-testimonials .jdgm-rev__rating .jdgm-star { color: #F5A623 !important; }
.ps-testimonials .jdgm-rev { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border) !important; }
.ps-testimonials .jdgm-rev__author { font-weight: 800 !important; color: var(--lav-ink) !important; }
.ps-testimonials .jdgm-rev__body { color: var(--lav-ink) !important; line-height: 1.6 !important; }
.ps-testimonials .jdgm-all-reviews-text-summary { color: var(--lav) !important; font-family: 'Luckiest Guy', cursive !important; letter-spacing: .04em !important; }
</style>
